{"tid":1025874,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文][求救]女友老母信埋唔知咩教 真系搞到人都癲","createTime":"2019-02-17T15:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T16:40:07.000Z","uid":80562,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c5dca59b44561ad97f4b12845b816a4f6e1d74f","tid":1025874,"uid":80562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"講講背景先 同女友拍拖三年左右 相安無事 發展穩定 <br />\n<br />\n唯一就系佢呀媽奇奇怪怪 唔知信埋大陸啲咩師父 係咁話我唔好 超反對我地 明明見都未見過 認識都未認識過 仲講到千祈唔好帶我上女友屋企 如果唔係就反面 <br />\n<br />\n係咁嘅情況底下 我只好用行動同時間證明 對佢個女好好 過時過節都會買啲野 叫女友拎番屋企 (雖然好似唔知係我買嘅)<br />\n<br />\n好啦 問題黎啦 佢信埋啲咩都唔緊要 做咩要迫佢個女信 又祈埋啲咩繩 咩彿珠 咩符 一定要我女友帶 都算 當系飾物 一番心意 當祈福 試過離譜到求埋啲咩符水要女友飲 好彩女友扮飲 然後倒左佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今個星期仲癲 拎左女友一件衛衣番大陸 比師父 作法 轉運 要佢今個星期番工著<br />\n<br />\n如果個師父真系呃錢都好啲 最怕件衫唔知有咩 會唔會落左啲咩降頭又唔知 (利申 完全唔識咩降頭個啲點落 )<br />\n最怕係有菌 我女友有好嚴重皮膚感敏 試過敏感到眼腫 呼吸困難 入院<br />\n<br />\n一陣件衫有咩皮膚病 著左上身 點搞？<br />\n<br />\n而家女友話著出門口 之後去廁所換左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有咩建議 同知唔知拎件衫作法係咩一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7716abd3187196c0c99b40aece83625f2ccebd7","tid":1025874,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"叫佢老公屌醒佢啦屌"},{"pid":"a97a355b2a07f6f3d3a05b266be7ef15bdb86ec1","tid":1025874,"uid":80562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7716abd3187196c0c99b40aece83625f2ccebd7","tid":1025874,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"叫佢老公屌醒佢啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"女友 : 佢老公已經放棄左 搞唔到佢 多數當見唔到 置身事外"},{"pid":"761e2c47d83de84256430d69afcc5ec21184f994","tid":1025874,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"我都畀你啲5p字搞到人都癲<br />\n一時係一時系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c91d1023a9c324f814edf1396c212f110b071e8","tid":1025874,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:38:37.000Z","msg":"南無超<br />\n殊樂嗶嗶"},{"pid":"0ffb61e7d46bf13d5035200e89a86b6aed8f1fbe","tid":1025874,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}